{"tid":1005431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！中糧集團證實購買過百萬噸美國大豆","createTime":"2019-02-02T08:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T09:23:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3f4f6aba215c29b9f6f0a13f087612f8f415c2","tid":1005431,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"中糧集團在官方網站宣布，為落實中美兩國元首達成的共識，早前已分批採購數百萬噸美國大豆的基礎上，近日，再次採購上百萬噸美國大豆。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前引述消息報道，在中美經貿會談結束之後，有交易商透露，中國購買的大豆合共約220萬噸，另有兩名交易商表示，中國的採購數由100萬噸至150萬噸，是近期三次採購量的總和。報道表示，中國採購美國大豆的訂單，將安排在四月及六月付運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441225-20190202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441225-20190202.htm&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2cpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=f01c0d05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441225-20190202.htm&h=9f06fd6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441225-20190202.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0b484d21a92ec576381ab096a6a8820dbb83c2b2","tid":1005431,"uid":170249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"說好的每天500萬噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d5fd9c76f4244d991f098636258c667ad426f1","tid":1005431,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"人人有豆食<br />\n中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"dfe299c9ac36d6206a50e0aba1305b97496a88ce","tid":1005431,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b484d21a92ec576381ab096a6a8820dbb83c2b2","tid":1005431,"uid":170249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"說好的每天500萬噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"說好的今天500萬噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{